description: Beautifully updated top-floor 2-bedroom condo just steps from M Street Beach! Enjoy your own private roof deck with stunning harbor views, perfect for relaxing or entertaining. The renovated kitchen features high-end cabinetry, granite countertops, gas cooking, and opens to a cozy living area with cherry hardwood floors, dining nook, and wood-burning fireplace. The spacious primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet plus a second large closet. A second bedroom with large closet is located off the main hall. Includes a huge deeded storage space and private laundry in the basement. Flat-screen TV and Bose surround sound system included. Prime East Side location, close to the beach, shops, restaurants, and all that South Boston has to offer!
